{"tid":2409903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登首現G7 商對華經濟策略","createTime":"2021-02-16T07:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T02:51:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9364b442d84e1780fc6319afe754e96b6fd6e892","tid":2409903,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:28:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210216/PSEBYKAVUJGM5HDPHVR7CWCSME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210216%2FPSEBYKAVUJGM5HDPHVR7CWCSME%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bj2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=59f06fb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210216%2FPSEBYKAVUJGM5HDPHVR7CWCSME%2F&h=92d72567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210216/PSEBYKAVUJGM5HDPHVR7CWCSME/</a><br />\n<br />\n拜登首現G7 商對華經濟策略<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ExDZa5RX1iptof7Z_eAJ4FWECVs=/1233x788/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CSI5FDGMQBDHDPNNO5IPGJBNII.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FExDZa5RX1iptof7Z_eAJ4FWECVs%3D%2F1233x788%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCSI5FDGMQBDHDPNNO5IPGJBNII.jpg&h=859bdf13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拜登<br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登料於美國時間周五首度出席七大工業國組織（G7）領導人視像會議，白宮透露，今次成員國將商討三大議題，包括如何應對中國的經濟挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冀救疫市 定全球秩序<br />\n<br />\n今次是自去年4月開始，G7成員首次召開會議，主要討論武漢肺炎病毒疫情、重建全球經濟計劃，以及共同應對中國。白宮發聲明指：「今次視像會議會為拜登提供機會，商討如何擊敗疫情，重建全球經濟。」就疫情方面，七國成員會主力討論疫苗生產及分配問題。各成員亦會討論中國問題，白宮指：「拜登會討論如何透過投資，增加成員國的競爭力。拜登亦希望制訂全球秩序，應對中國在經濟上的挑戰。」<br />\n<br />\n台灣問題目前亦是全球應對中國的重點之一，全球最重要的安全論壇，慕尼黑安全會議（Munich Security Conference）將在本周五（19日）揭幕，會議主席伊辛格（Wolfgang Ischinger）警告，台灣是目前最有可能發生軍事衝突的地方，他呼籲歐美就中國問題上加強協調，指出只要大陸與台灣衝突加劇，美國台灣派遣航空母艦前往南海為協防，將導致中國鼓勵俄羅斯出兵阻止美軍前進東亞，屆時整個歐洲會被捲進衝突。由於拜登上任前表明銳意改善美歐關係，應對中國挑戰，故今次會議走向深受各界關注。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"a995bf942d34190b94a243e7182a322f18f9dbeb","tid":2409903,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T08:17:51.000Z","msg":"個會有joe主持大局我就放心喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cc248f925b3d0df3e2a2bf9c93ec6a04a4a161","tid":2409903,"uid":183758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:31:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">食屎啦廢閪拜登<br />\n<br />\n歐盟即刻柴你台而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"035f61f7aeea2c11465c89868236ff0880fd925d","tid":2409903,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"塊面咁紅？"},{"pid":"4e8007a7d4eddc41c6cb2b74daac4872cd0a0eb7","tid":2409903,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"035f61f7aeea2c11465c89868236ff0880fd925d","tid":2409903,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"塊面咁紅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:33:36.000Z","msg":"喝酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718c0a4f3447ea799a3bcb58e003130bc1705363","tid":2409903,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"加強投資中國以建立美國在華影響力 實現對華現代化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用返英文直譯中文先夠共味"},{"pid":"bc7e3a3775198b180917883af74e72c175adb49f","tid":2409903,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"035f61f7aeea2c11465c89868236ff0880fd925d","tid":2409903,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"塊面咁紅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:37:10.000Z","msg":"中風先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mous